==Features ==
=== Flying seeds ===
[[File:Sketchu Spring Seeds.webp|thumb|A flying seed|195x195px]]In multiple areas of the world, spawners can be found that spawn seed-shaped devices that when sat in, can be controlled by the interactable handle to fly across the world. When a user exits a flying seed, it will instantly despawn. Flying seeds can be used as an effective method of traversing the world as they are significantly faster than the user's walk or run speed.